name: You had one job!
overview: Game made for commodore 64 in assembler lang by Krzysztof Kluczek, Aleksandra Krzyszewska, Denys Stanislavskyi & Michal Zuchowski. Two "professionals" have to hide what they screwed before house owner spot this. F1, and F3 on commodore 64 and emulators will change level, or restart game. Released for Global Game Jam 2020.
